          <Textbox Name="Textbox4">
            <CanGrow>true</CanGrow>
            <KeepTogether>true</KeepTogether>
            <Paragraphs>
              <Paragraph>
                <TextRuns>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value>Employees and manager determine and agree on goals for the next performance cycle. Goals need to be aligned to overall business objectives for the program or department, in line with employee’s roles and responsibilities. For clarity of expectations, the goals need to be SMART - Specific, Measurable, Attainable, Realistic, and Timely. To facilitate employee development/improvement, one of the objectives should a personal development goals. </Value>
                    <Style>
                      <FontFamily>Calibri</FontFamily>
                      <FontSize>11pt</FontSize>
                    </Style>
                  </TextRun>
                </TextRuns>
                <Style />
              </Paragraph>
            </Paragraphs>
            <rd:DefaultName>Textbox4</rd:DefaultName>
            <Top>1.92014in</Top>
            <Left>0.13069in</Left>
            <Height>0.88194in</Height>
            <Width>11.27083in</Width>
            <ZIndex>1</ZIndex>
